lead_paragraph: Governor Chris Christie pushed past a sea of angry protesters on Monday to meet with business leaders and politicians on ways to save troubled Atlantic City, which has lost a quarter of its 12 casinos already this year.

headline.main: Governor Christie on Atlantic City Casinos Closures: We Have Work to Do
headline.print_headline: Governor Christie on Atlantic City Casinos Closures: We Have Work to Do
